section.def:
Authority
                (委員會) means the Housing Authority established
            under section 3;

housing
                (房屋) means residential, industrial, commercial
            and business accommodation, buildings or premises;

paragraph.content:
to acquire and hold property of any description and, subject to the terms
                    and conditions upon which the same is held, to dispose of any such
                    property;

to act as agent for the Government in respect of the sale and development
                    of any land, including the nomination of purchasers in respect of land leased
                    from the Government; (Added 15 of 1982 s. 4. Amended 29 of 1998 s. 105)

subsection.def:
committee
                    (小組委員會) means a committee appointed under
                    section 7;

functions
                    (職能) includes, in relation to the Director of
                Housing, duties;

paragraph.content:
in relation to the first review of the relevant rent after
                            1 January 2010,
                        means a period of 12 months expiring on 31 December 2007;

subsection.def:
land
                    (土地) does not include land in respect of
                which the Authority has granted to a person a licence, or a permit, to occupy;

paragraph.content:
in relation to the first review of the relevant rent after
                            1 January 2010,
                        means a period of 12 months expiring on 31 December 2009;

in respect of an application for a lease;
                        or (Amended 16 of
                            1993 s. 11)

subparagraph.content:
the person entering into the provisional agreement for sale and
                        purchase as the purchaser is certified by the Authority as a person eligible
                        to buy relevant land;

paragraph.content:
the purchaser shall pay to the Authority at the same time as he submits his
                    application for the assessment, an administrative fee set and published by the
                    Authority;
